<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wardrive Data Visualization</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Wardrive Data Visualization</h1>
            <p>Laden Sie Wardrive-Logdateien hoch und visualisieren Sie die Daten auf der Karte</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="upload-section">
                <h2>Datei hochladen</h2>
                <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <input type="file" name="wardriveFile" accept=".log" required>
                    <button type="submit">Hochladen</button>
                </form>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; background: #111; border-radius: 3px;">
                    <h3>Info</h3>
                    <p>Akzeptierte Formate: .log-Dateien im WigleWifi-Format</p>
                    <p>Unterst√ºtzte Auth-Modi:</p>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <li><span style="color: orange;">‚óè</span> WPA2_PSK</li>
                        <li><span style="color: red;">‚óè</span> WPA2_WPA3_PSK</li>
                        <li><span style="color: green;">‚óè</span> OPEN</li>
                        <li><span style="color: gray;">‚óè</span> Andere</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="data-section">
                <h2>Verf√ºgbare Datens√§tze</h2>
                <% if (files && files.length > 0) { %>
                    <form id="datasetForm">
                        <select name="dataset" id="datasetSelect">
                            <% files.forEach(file => { %>
                                <option value="<%= file.table_name %>"><%= file.filename %> (<%= new Date(file.upload_time).toLocaleDateString('de-DE') %>)</option>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                        <button type="button" id="loadDataBtn">Daten laden</button>
                    </form>
                    
                    
                    <div id="mapContainer">
                        <div id="map"></div>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; background: #111; border-radius: 3px;">
                        <p>Keine Datens√§tze verf√ºgbar. Laden Sie eine Wardrive-Logdatei hoch.</p>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 3em;">üì°</p>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #333;">
            <p>Wardrive Data Visualization | Built with Node.js, Express, PostgreSQL & Leaflet | by bmetallica.de</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/map.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
